import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Card, Container, Header, Label, Image, Divider, Icon} from 'semantic-ui-react'


export default class StoryDetail extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
    <Container>
      <Header style={{color:'white'}} > Events </Header>
      <Card.Group itemsPerRow={5} stackable>
      <Card  onClick={()=>alert("MEMES")} fluid style = {{  backgroundColor: "#4c4c4c", boxShadow:"none",  borderRadius: '25px'}} raised >  
        <Image src= "http://localhost:5000/images/progress.png" width={'100%'} height={200}/>
    
        <Card.Content  fluid   >
          
          <Card.Header style = {{color:'white'}}> First Card</Card.Header>
          <Card.Meta>
            
            <Label >04/20/2019</Label>
    
          </Card.Meta>
          
          <Card.Description  style = {{color:'#7a7a7a '}} >sadsadasd</Card.Description>
        </Card.Content>
     
    
    
        
      </Card>
      

      <Card  onClick={()=>alert("MEMES")} fluid style = {{  backgroundColor: "#4c4c4c", boxShadow:"none",  borderRadius: '25px'}} raised >  
        <Image src= "http://localhost:5000/images/progress.png" width={'100%'} height={200}/>
    
        <Card.Content  fluid   >
          
          <Card.Header style = {{color:'white'}}> First Card</Card.Header>
          <Card.Meta>
            
            <Label >04/20/2019</Label>
    
          </Card.Meta>
          
          <Card.Description  style = {{color:'#7a7a7a '}} >sadsadasd</Card.Description>
        </Card.Content>
     
    
    
        
      </Card>
      
  </Card.Group>
    </Container>

    )
  }
}
